column2: SELECT sp.ra,sp.dec,sp.z, sp.plate, sp.fiberid,sp.mjd,   sp.modelMag_i AS mag_i , sp.modelMag_g AS mag_g, sp.modelMag_r AS mag_r, sp.fiberMag_i,   sp.CModelMag_i AS cmag_i , sp.CMODELMag_g AS cmag_g, sp.CMODELMag_r AS cmag_r     FROM SpecPhotoAll AS sp into mydb.CLQ_gal     WHERE       ( sp.class = &&& and ap.MJD > #)
